messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "正确识别营销规划意图",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块将明确的营销规划请求错误归类为“其他意图”（intent:4001），未匹配到预期的营销意图码。可能原因包括意图分类 prompt 对“NBEV”“增加理财师”“优化产品方案”等营销信号覆盖不足，或模型输出未对齐预定义意图集。",
      "evidence": [
        {"field": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent", "value": "4001"},
        {"field": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent_name", "value": "其他意图"},
        {"probe": "planning_output_probe.actual_stage", "value": null},
        {"probe": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition.evidence.actual_stage", "value": "non_agent"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "进入正确的agent阶段",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "场景路由依赖意图识别结果，由于意图被误判为“其他意图”，系统将阶段指派为 non_agent，而非期望的 intent 或 planning 阶段。意图识别输出直接导致阶段路由错误。",
      "evidence": [
        {"field": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage", "value": "non_agent"},
        {"probe": "planning_output_probe.stage_match", "value": false},
        {"reference": "reference_contract.expected_stage", "value": "intent"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "SSE事件序列完整且业务完成标志正确",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["sse_generation", "intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "sse_generation 阶段在业务实际失败（意图错误，无有效卡片）的情况下仍将 business_completed 置为 true，未能反映服务真实状态。该错误或源于生成逻辑未校验下游业务结果，且与上游意图识别失败导致的空结果直接相关。",
      "evidence": [
        {"field": "extracted_output.turns[0].event_summary.business_completed", "value": true},
        {"field": "extracted_output.turns[0].event_summary.completed", "value": true},
        {"probe": "execution_stage_probe.planning_function.evidence.card_count", "value": 0}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "Reference contract 要求当前场景为 intent 阶段，但 intent_recognition 的输出 stage 为 non_agent，直接违反合同约定，导致整条链路无法按预期执行。",
      "evidence": [
        {"field": "reference_contract.expected_stage", "value": "intent"},
        {"field": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage", "value": "non_agent"},
        {"probe": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition.evidence.actual_stage", "value": "non_agent"}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "在 intent_recognition 阶段，系统将用户明显属于营销规划范畴的请求（通过增加理财师或优化产品方案弥补NBEV）错误分类为“其他意图”（intent:4001），并据此将 stage 设置为 non_agent。这导致后续所有规划相关路径（path_dispatch、planning_function 等）均未执行，最终输出完全偏离 reference contract（期望 stage=intent）。虽然该阶段被标记为执行成功，但其输出内容已造成业务阻断，是整个链路最早且最根本的失败点。SSE 的 business_completed 错误也源于此空流程。",
  "evidence": [
    {"source": "judge_result", "finding": "用户询问通过增加理财师或优化产品方案弥补NBEV差距，明显属于营销规划范畴，但 intent 被识别为 4001（其他意图），stage 为 non_agent。"},
    {"source": "judge_result.missing", "items": ["missing_correct_intent", "missing_correct_stage"]},
    {"source": "judge_result.wrong", "items": ["wrong_intent", "wrong_stage", "wrong_business_completed_flag"]},
    {"source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition", "evidence": "actual_stage: non_agent, expected_stage: intent"},
    {"source": "planning_output_probe", "evidence": "actual_stage: null, stage_match: false, card_count: 0"},
    {"source": "execution_trace.planning_function", "evidence": "card_count: 0"},
    {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent", "value": "4001"},
    {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].intent_name", "value": "其他意图"},
    {"source": "extracted_output.turns[0].stage", "value": "non_agent"}
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

